result.name: Goobne Chicken - Hongkong Causeway Bay

reviews.text: Can't stop coming back to Goobne! Authentic new and trendy Korean food with an amazing view. Restaurant staff and order system is very cool with buttons to ring up servers so you never miss a beat. Location is great and one of my favorite group hangout spots. Their air fried chicken is also a great alternative to oil fried chicken to friends who are craving fried chicken on a diet!

Korean chicken. No doubt that it is a very famous food in Korea. Lucky they make it available in HK. The spicy is very spicy. Make sure you can afford the spicy. Or you need lots of cold drink with it. It has a nice view too. I prefer the sun day light instead of the night view. Go enjoy it.
Way better than Dodam down the street! Spacious seating. Friendly service but not attentive enough eventhough lots of staff. Good taste. Average prices.

saw this advertised on Instagram. Me and my partner went to the Causewaybay branch and tried the UFO Cheese Fondue Chicken. It was good. Service is also good. View was excellent if placed by the window side.

The food is actually quite nice, but the service is quite horrible. I seldom complain about the service because i know everyone has a hard time, especially for those who work for long hours, but the service is just...

reviews.text: 多款式又好食😋

食物還可以但是女店員態度很差
我一坐下就問女服務員有沒有菜單
（因為我看桌上只有Drinks)
然後女服務員很跩的說
這就是菜單（還用丟的！）然後轉身就走
幹 阿明明桌上就是飲料單
我後來又叫了一個男服務員
問說請問有菜單嗎
男服務員默默從隔壁桌拿了菜單
：說不好意思 妳桌上兩本都是飲料單
那女店員是有什麼問題？真的是欠人家投訴
心不甘情不願就不要做服務業
光看妳那厭世臉加上那個態度 
我就不會再來了
我沒記名字 反正就是一個女的臉最臭的就是她了
我也懶得當下叫經理出來
因為叫了也沒用

result.name: V-Point

reviews.text: One of the new high rise building consisting of upmarket restaurants.

I had only one drink there, so I can't say much about the food but the view is pretty good and the staff was super friendly. They even made some discount on the occasion of my b-day and offered some shots. I thinks its definitely worth trying, at least, once)
When i asked the concierge where the washroom is , they said there is no washroom in the whole plaza... this is so weird
Great location near Times Square and with a number of eateries, including good Japanese ones like Ootoya.
Is a brand-new landmark in Causeway Bay, surrounded by top restaurants and top fitness centres, highly recommended!!

reviews.text:
豫園 (銅鑼灣)
銅鑼灣登龍街18號 V Point 26樓

招牌松子鮮魚最開胃，可以加碗白飯送汁!

今天本來是去吃火鍋的，不過朋友病了轉了中餐。朋友本來電話去訂位說沒有位不能預訂，但之後我們walk in就有位。這家餐廳是全層分左面廳，右面廳。左面廳全部沒有景，右面廳裝修非常華麗。如果真的要去吃就要訂有景的一邊。

食物方面，我覚得整體ok, 我特別喜歡招牌松子魚，酸酸甜甜一整條，好味。脆皮素鴨也很出色。

如果想食高力豆沙或豆沙鍋餅就要預早叫定好樣廚房準備。那天我們大約10:30pm叫這兩款甜品，全都沒有！
One of the new high rise building consisting of upmarket restaurants.
餐飲為主，但宣傳唔多，下面又冇餐牌可以睇
貴價又難食的高檔菜式

I had only one drink there, so I can't say much about the food but the view is pretty good and the staff was super friendly. They even made some discount on the occasion of my b-day and offered some shots. I thinks its definitely worth trying, at least, once)
